node.text:
The popular Jupiter Shield theory proposes that the planet acts like a giant space shield due to its huge mass causing it to suck in or deflect dangerous debris that might be heading towards Earth.

However, this theory is on shaky grounds due to new contradicting evidence. 🌍🔭

Do you love space? Follow @Spacespot ✨
Space store 👉 @Spacespotshop

📸: @spaceytales
